<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer16115580587363346005">Aron Hector Schmitz, better known by the pseudonym Italo Svevo was an Italian writer, businessman, novelist, playwright, and short story writer.<br/><br/>A close friend of Irish novelist and poet James Joyce, Svevo was considered a pioneer of the psychological novel in Italy and is best known for his classic modernist novel La coscienza di Zeno (1923), a work that had a profound effect on the movement.</span>

</div>
</div>

